{"tid":609123,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講個笑話你聽 肥婆話減肥","createTime":"2018-03-28T17:58:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-11T17:25:25.000Z","uid":59748,"like":10,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6444bd107986c3a00f19cb2694fdaa0430cc62c9","tid":609123,"uid":59748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T17:58:07.000Z","msg":"我係一個水腫難分嘅肥婆<br />\n但好撚搞鬼嘅係 我淨係肥下身<br />\n上身就好標準 條腰最瘦試過23.5吋  <br />\n我157cm 體重50～51kg 遊走<br />\n最輕試過46kg 最重試過53kg <br />\n但對腳係咁多年都冇變過 都係咁肉<br />\n我諗係遺傳基因太強大 我媽咪係一個肥妹仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係咩方法都試過曬咁濟（除咗食藥）<br />\n運動 飲食控制 飲紅豆水 燃燒脂肪揸嘅藥膏 中醫調理都試埋 都係唔得<br />\n減咗咁多年 真係心都灰埋<br />\n又話冇肥女人 只有懶女人嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢排聽朋友講其實我唔可以靜係掛住做帶氧 <br />\n所以呢次嘅減行動操埋肌肉 去做gym 同深蹲<br />\n今次想開post 想記錄下成敗 順便督促下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都想有巴絲分享減肥經歷 參考又好 當俾啲希望自己又好 拯救下小女子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n肥婆示意圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/29/014806_63e54bd2f95d6e4d5f6f65e4ea24e9fe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F29%2F014806_63e54bd2f95d6e4d5f6f65e4ea24e9fe.png&h=d0f8541d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我exac7ly 係左三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能有啲會話 下 唔係好肥姐 <br />\n但夏天係唔敢著短褲出街 啲大脾肉磨下磨下 好撚辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋成個比例好撚怪 上瘦下肥睇落再粗啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過我係冇咁易打得沉 今次唔得下次一定得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇人睇冇人理我都會堅持落去 有朝一日我會瘦到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽朝跑步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194b09174dea5ecf9f48f42668eaf53c288c6248","tid":609123,"uid":16772,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T17:59:49.000Z","msg":"吓 我覺得對腳粗粗地先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96fdd1be19f883779dfe67bdc44fc6a66c082d5","tid":609123,"uid":125079,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T18:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都叫肥....最多叫偏重姐"},{"pid":"c57074b0933f0cbadcb1c39656e684dbd1534b72","tid":609123,"uid":59748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"194b09174dea5ecf9f48f42668eaf53c288c6248","tid":609123,"uid":16772,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T17:59:49.000Z","msg":"吓 我覺得對腳粗粗地先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T18:02:43.000Z","msg":"你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔要聽呢啲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187c3d5bc75b326f8a02253b488a46946dd48bdc","tid":609123,"uid":59748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b96fdd1be19f883779dfe67bdc44fc6a66c082d5","tid":609123,"uid":125079,"like":7,"dislike":3,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T18:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁都叫肥....最多叫偏重姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T18:03:59.000Z","msg":"因為比例真係好怪 對腳好粗"},{"pid":"dc84cb2bcfdfc33ed28d8bd687e8a4c6bca2d31d","tid":609123,"uid":105552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl